Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第20章 爱人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.08,0:23:37.08,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}协力：jabal taburiss 绿叶之砚 Oilon 冷たぃ海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记那略带机油味的甘甜芬芳
